name: Through the Spectrum by Willea Zwey

metadata.name: Through the Spectrum (+)Y3
metadata.description: An art experiment where artistic expression meets social interconnectivity. This collection consists of 50 individually developed artworks that play with visual parameters originating from a single blueprint. With a reimagination of the language of color, each variation results in a unique aesthetic throughout the entire collection. Each NFT becomes a standalone work of art, while celebrating their shared origin.
